Usage: hunt &lt;player/monster&gt;<br/>
This is a powerful skill which, like track, enables the user to find his prey.<br/>
However, hunt will allow you to quickly follow the person automatically, and<br/>
should you find him/her, it will make you engage him/her in combat.<br/>
